  "texts": [
    "The dashed black line indicates the inferred counterfactual for the treated group had GitHub Copilot not been introduced.",
    "To analyze how LLMs affect different types of innovation, we employ two complementary approaches: analyzing function additions in code diffs (Section 5.2.1) and examining LLM-categorized commit messages (Section 5.2.2).",
    "For both approaches, we run separate analyses for each innovation type by employing equation (1) and replacing the dependent variable with 𝑌!$\" 3, where v represents the categorization type (function addition or LLM categorized), i represent the package, t indexes the quarter and j indexes the innovation type (with vs. without new function, or code development vs. maintenance).",
    "Commits with new Function added vs.",
    "Commits without."
